configurationElements.name: PRODUCT_REVISION

configurationElements.name: SWUPD_EXT
configurationElements.description: The software update file extension.

configurationElements.name: TYPE
configurationElements.description: Defines the image type.

configurationElements.name: USE_OVERRIDE
configurationElements.description: Define whether the override.pm Buildrom.pl plugin is used (Includes automatically also \epoc32\rom\override.oby).

configurationElements.name: USE_PAGING
configurationElements.description: Define the usage of On Demand Pagin (ODP). (E.g. 0,rom,code).

configurationElements.name: USE_ROFS

configurationElements.name: USE_ROMFILE
